name: Space Rocket (itch) (Blukulele)
description:
🚀  🚀  🚀

Navigate in your rocket to reach the end of space!

Go through black holes, gather a lot of stars and avoid obstacles!

  • Up arrow key to move forward
  • Left / Right arrow to rotate

A game made in 3 hours for the Trijam #121. The theme was "Exploring spacetime". Hope you like it!

🚀  🚀  🚀
